```

**에러 처리 패턴**:
```kotlin
try {
    val result = service.getFeature(request.id)
    responseObserver.onNext(result.toProtoResponse())
    responseObserver.onCompleted()
} catch (e: NotFoundException) {
    responseObserver.onError(
        Status.NOT_FOUND
            .withDescription(e.message)
            .asRuntimeException()
    )
}
```

